title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 235-1.1 - Applicability
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 235-1.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

Except as provided in Subpart 235-4 of this Part, this

Part shall apply to any person who sells, supplies, offers for sale, or
manufactures consumer products for use in the State of New

York. Notes
